Proxmox Datacenter Manager (Docker)
===================================

This project packages Proxmox Datacenter Manager into a container image. It is an
unofficial, community-maintained build and is not affiliated with, nor endorsed
by, Proxmox Server Solutions GmbH.

Packaging files in this repository
----------------------------------
The packaging files authored here (Dockerfile, entrypoint.sh,
disable-subscription-nag.html, docker-compose.yml, workflows) are licensed under
the MIT License. See the LICENSE file.

Bundled third-party software
----------------------------
The container image installs, unmodified, the official Proxmox `.deb` packages
from http://download.proxmox.com/debian/pdm:

  - proxmox-datacenter-manager-container-meta
  - proxmox-datacenter-manager-ui
  - and their dependencies

These packages, and Proxmox Datacenter Manager itself, are
Copyright (C) Proxmox Server Solutions GmbH and are distributed under the
GNU Affero General Public License, version 3 (AGPL-3.0).
See https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html

Corresponding source code for these AGPL components is published by Proxmox and
available at:

  - https://git.proxmox.com/            (upstream source repositories)
  - http://download.proxmox.com/debian/pdm   (binary and source packages)

No Proxmox source code is modified by this project. The image runs the official
binaries; only the startup process is adapted for a container environment.

